O '''Apolima''' o le motu i [[Samoa]] i le itumalo o [[Aiga-i-le-Tai]].

E tasi le tama'i nu'u i le motu, e igoa ia Apolima Tai. E le to'atele ni tagata e nonofo i le motu, e atoa le 75 o tagata. <ref>[http://www.sbs.gov.ws/Portals/138/PDF/census%20survey/Table%202.%20Population%20byregion,%20faipule%20district%202006.pdf] Tusigaigoa o tagata ma fale 2006, Ofisa o Fuainumera ma Fa'amaumauga Matagaluega o Tupe. Sa'ili'ili 2 Fepuari, 2010</ref>

